comment: The caramel flavor is borderline too sweet. There is still just a little whiskey type sting to it. Definitely a good after dinner dessert sipper. It could also be a good introduction to those that are new to (or previously turned away from,) the taste of whiskey & bourbon.
Delicious and complex. Distinct whiskey and caramel flavors
Wow you definitely taste what it claims to be, salted caramel with the whiskey smooth burn. Maybe a little too sweet for my tastes but a great after dinner dessert whiskey!
